{"tid":1060934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個唔想生仔，一個好想生仔。將來究竟有冇希望","createTime":"2019-03-14T05:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T09:37:09.000Z","uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"845a2e7cfa57dffb256cb788d8f1102c975c5446","tid":1060934,"uid":130601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:03:14.000Z","msg":"我好想有小朋友，但我女朋友唔係太想生。究竟我哋將來仲有冇希望<br />\n<br />\n巴絲打們你地身邊有冇呢d case"},{"pid":"072a35a15f59df158cc0141ad6e6ec010aa9541c","tid":1060934,"uid":799,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"換女"},{"pid":"ab49a5ea9b8d3c55034409f0dc12fa6bf1e31eb4","tid":1060934,"uid":130601,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"拍左2年拖，我今日28歲，佢25。我諗都差不多係時候諗下將來，只係傾下計咁plan下。<br />\n佢成日都話唔想傾，唔通拍拖拍到3x歲咩。佢話一講呢d野就唔開心，咁人生係要諗呢d架喎。<br />\n大家拍拖玩樂開心，呢排講下d將來野就咁。唉，我好鐘意呢個女朋友，想同佢生兒育女，有個美夢既家庭。<br />\n<br />\n我唔想過多3-4年，佢都成30歲既時候先分手，對女仔好傷"},{"pid":"3cb87e15c8bbccb5dc5f0e3ae424b1cc8dcde8b1","tid":1060934,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:14:09.000Z","msg":"冇希望 分手啦"},{"pid":"3ee93db88f6e8041ef21677e0d6027b66eb8ce69","tid":1060934,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"依家分手囉 你條女無撚腦"},{"pid":"39935b2715cbd9cd8c59b6b1671a30935e8de71b","tid":1060934,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"標題應該係改為 一個有計劃將來 同一個唔會計劃將來嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得女方唔係你想揾嘅終身對像 佢似係未玩夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22582355296826d5d3babb12c0a6a4edad857180","tid":1060934,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"點解拍左2年都唔攤牌"},{"pid":"5a66d7c24cff3da80b6236c645fa8e9a59f61abb","tid":1060934,"uid":10195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39935b2715